        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>International&#174; 7000 model trucks, used in some applications, may have a damaged turbocharger
                    inlet hose caused by exhaust manifold heat. A heat shield kit is available, if needed, to protect
                    the turbocharger inlet hose from exhaust manifold heat.
                </para>
